name: NBCNews
text:
People trying to kill the coronavirus with ultraviolet C germicidal lamps may risk painful eye injuries if they aren't careful, a recent study finds. 

The eye damage is "like a sunburn to the cornea," one ophthalmologist says. https://t.co/CfBV21Bm07

name: NBCNews
text:
15 members of one family got Covid-19 after a small gathering.

“My family has taken every single precaution with the exception of one and that exception has cost us so much,” says Alexa Aragonez. https://t.co/aE238OjvWH
